===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|ἐπιστήμη||science, knowledge}}, from {{m|grc|ἐπίσταμαι||I know}} + {{m|grc|-λογία||discourse}}, from {{m|grc|λέγω||I speak}}. The term was introduced into English by the Scottish philosopher James Frederick Ferrier (1808-1864).

